        </div>

        <div class="glass review-card fade-up">

            <div class="review-header">
                <div class="avatar">A</div>
                <div>
                    <h4>Amit Verma</h4>
                    <span>Verified Buyer</span>
                </div>
            </div>

            ★★★★☆
            <p>Great bike but mileage could improve slightly.</p>

        </div>

    </div>

</section>

<!-- FAQ -->
<section id="faq" class="section">

    <div class="section-title fade-up">FAQ</div>

    <div class="faq-container">

        <div class="faq-item glass fade-up">
            <button class="faq-question">What is mileage?</button>
            <div class="faq-answer">
                KTM 390 Duke delivers around 28–30 kmpl depending on riding style.
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item glass fade-up">
            <button class="faq-question">Does it have quickshifter?</button>
            <div class="faq-answer">
                Yes, Quick Shifter+ is available in this model.
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item glass fade-up">
            <button class="faq-question">Fuel tank capacity?</button>
            <div class="faq-answer">
                15 litres.
            </div>
        </div>

    </div>

</section>

<!-- FOOTER -->
<footer>
    <div class="footer-logo">KTM Luxury</div>
    <p>Premium Motorcycle Experience</p>
    <p>© 2026 All Rights Reserved</p>
</footer>

